//  5. Envelope-vs-payload version decoupling ..... protocol_version ≠ ContractRef.sha256
//  6. Provenance core-stamped, not plugin-claimed  NO provenance field exists (by design)
//  7. Idempotency-by-contract + checkpoint/resume  Envelope.idempotency_key + ApplyRequest.resume_token
//  8. Cursor-delta Observe + content-hash ........ ObserveRequest.cursor + Envelope.content_hash
//  9. Observe tree at true bands + atomic Apply .. Item.children + Apply on the root
// 10. One bus + typed plugin classes ............. this single service + Manifest.class
// 11. Facet-ownership + coordinate-scope pre-write  core-side check on every returned Envelope (note)
// 12. Typed, core-legible diagnostic descent ..... TaskEvent is typed, NOT an opaque blob
// 13. SDK stays permissively licensed ............ out-of-band (the shipped SDK links no copyleft)
